quran[9]{c,v,t,f}:
  23,106,"Wọ́n wí pé: “Olúwa wa, orí burúkú ló kọlù wá; àwa sì jẹ́ ìjọ olùṣìnà."
  23,107,"Olúwa wa, mú wa jáde kúrò nínú Iná. Tí a bá fi lè padà (síbi iṣẹ́ ibi nílé ayé), dájúdájú nígbà náà alábòsí ni àwa.”"
  23,108,"(Allāhu) sọ pé: “Ẹ tẹ̀rì sínú rẹ̀. Ẹ má ṣe bá Mi sọ̀rọ̀.”"
  25,52,"Nítorí náà, má ṣe tẹ̀lé àwọn aláìgbàgbọ́. Kí o sì fi (al-Ƙur’ān) jà wọ́n ní ogun tó tóbi."
  25,53,"Òun ni Ẹni tí Ó mú àwọn odò méjì ṣàn kiri. Èyí (ni omi) tó dùn gan-an. Èyí sì (ni omi) iyọ̀ tó móró. Ó sì fi gàgá sí ààrin àwọn méjèèjì. (Ó sì) ṣe é ní èèwọ̀ pọ́nńbélé (fún wọn láti rò papọ̀ mọ́ra wọn)."
  25,54,"Òun ni Ẹni tí Ó ṣẹ̀dá abara láti inú omi. Ó ṣe ìbátan ẹbí àti ìbátan àna fún un, Olúwa rẹ sì ń jẹ́ Alágbára.{1}.",footnotes:1:Ìṣẹ̀dá ènìyàn wáyé nípasẹ̀ oríṣi ọ̀nà mẹ́rin ọ̀tọ̀ọ̀tọ̀. Ìkíní; nípasẹ̀ erùpẹ̀. Ìkejì; nípasẹ̀ ẹfọ́nhà. Ìkẹta; nípasẹ̀ omi àtọ̀. Ìkẹrin; nípasẹ̀ atẹ́gùn ẹ̀mí àti gbólóhùn “kunfayakūn” Rẹ̀.
  26,25,"(Fir‘aon) wí fún àwọn tó wà ní àyíká rẹ̀ pé: “Ṣé ẹ ẹ̀ gbọ́ ọ̀rọ̀ (tó ń sọ ni)?”"
  26,26,"(Ànábì Mūsā) sọ pé: “(Allāhu ni) Olúwa yín àti Olúwa àwọn bàbá yín, àwọn ẹni àkọ́kọ́.”"
  26,27,"(Fir‘aon) wí pé: “Dájúdájú Òjíṣẹ́ yín èyí tí wọ́n rán si yín, wèrè mà ni.”"